Package: stem
Version: __VERSION__
Architecture: __ARCHITECTURE__
Maintainer: Kris Armstrong <kris@mustardseednetworks.com>
Depends: systemd
Recommends: libcap2-bin, ufw
Description: The Stem - Network Performance Testing Tool by Mustard Seed Networks
 The Stem is a high-performance network testing tool supporting:
  - RFC 2544 benchmarking (throughput, latency, frame loss)
  - ITU-T Y.1564 service activation testing
  - ITU-T Y.1731 Ethernet OAM
  - Packet reflection for remote testing
  - WebUI, TUI, and CLI interfaces
 .
 Homepage: https://github.com/krisarmstrong/stem
